A schoolgirl, 14, hanged herself after her boyfriend she met on Facebook rejected her.

In a heartrending suicide note, the Indian teenager wrote before her death on Tuesday: 'I am ruined and have no interest in life.'

The child, who has not been named, dated the college student for two months and had sex with him.

